      "title": "The Clixerfy Fraudulent Click Blocker",
      "slug": "ad-fraud-blocker",
      "metaTitle": "Advanced Adfraud Blocker | Stop Fake Traffic & Save Ad Budget | Clixerfy",
      "metaDescription": "Protect your ad spend from bots, competitors, and click farms. Clixerfy Adfraud Blocker stops invalid traffic in real-time with direct ad platform API sync.",
      "herosection": [
        {
          "id": 18,
          "titleText": "Complete Ad Immunity",
          "subtitle": "Don't just track fraud. Terminate it. Clixerfy proactively detects and blocks sophisticated click fraud before it drains your marketing budget.\n",
          "richtext": null,
          "bgimage": null,
          "featuredimage": null,
          "__component": "shared.sections-about-hero"
        },
        {
          "id": 19,
          "titleText": "The Clixerfy Fraudulent Click Blocker: Complete Ad Immunity",
          "subtitle": "Don’t Just Track Fraud. Terminate It.",
          "richtext": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Most advertisers blindly rely on the basic \"Invalid Traffic\" filters provided natively by major ad networks. The problem? Those filters are built to protect the advertising platform's bottom line, not yours. While they catch basic, outdated bots, they leave your campaigns completely exposed to highly sophisticated, human-like click fraud."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clixerfy is your proactive defense system. Our advanced Adfraud Blocker acts as a 24/7 digital sentry. By analyzing visitor behavior in less than 100 milliseconds, we identify malicious intent and block threats before fake traffic drains your daily marketing budget."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "bgimage": "https://clixerfy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/The-Clixerfy-Fraudulent-Click-Blocker-Complete-Ad-Immunity.webp",
          "featuredimage": "https://clixerfy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Complete-Ad-Immunity.jpg",
          "__component": "shared.sections-about-hero"
        }
      ],
      "features": [
        {
          "id": 9,
          "sectionTitle": "Why Standard Filters Aren't Enough",
          "body": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Platform-native invalid traffic filters are naturally conservative. Ad networks only filter out traffic they are 100% certain is fraudulent to prevent \"False Positives\" (accidentally blocking an active buyer)."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Clixerfy puts the control back into your hands. We provide an adjustable protection toggle that allows your security or marketing teams to dial in exactly how aggressively to shield your pipeline:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            }
