      "Richtext": [
        {
          "id": 7,
          "title": "What We Block: The 4 Pillars of Click Fraud",
          "subtitle": null,
          "bodycontent": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Whether it is an automated script or a human actor trying to sabotage your campaign, Clixerfy mitigates the risk across four core areas:"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "child": [
            {
              "id": 25,
              "title": "1. Professional Competitor Attacks",
              "subtitle": "In highly competitive industries (such as Legal, Real Estate, Locksmiths, and SaaS), rival companies frequently click your ads to intentionally deplete your daily budget and push your business out of the search auctions.",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The Clixerfy Defense:",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " We track unique device architecture and repeat clickers originating from the same corporate networks and office IPs. Once an entity crosses your custom threshold (e.g., 3 clicks within 24 hours), they are instantly restricted from seeing your ads."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "bgimage": null,
              "icon": {
                "iconName": "arcticons:radiant-defense",
                "iconData": "<path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M16.082 12.681c3.282 0 5.936 2.654 5.936 5.936s-2.654 5.935-5.936 5.935s-5.946-2.653-5.946-5.935s2.664-5.936 5.946-5.936M25.82 9.67c2.708-1.928 6.953-.585 9.499 2.99c2.556 3.574 2.426 8.036-.271 9.954c-2.697 1.928-6.954.584-9.5-2.99c-2.544-3.574-2.425-8.037.272-9.954\"/><path fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M29.936 29.015v9.9c0 2.47 4.462 2.47 4.462 0V28.018q0-.985 1.484-.985c2.968 0 5.448-.986 4.95-5.936C38.85.301 9.15.301 7.168 21.097c-.498 4.95 1.982 5.936 4.95 5.936q1.484 0 1.484.986v10.896c0 2.47 4.462 2.47 4.462 0v-9.9c0-1.982 3.455-1.982 3.455 0v10.886c0 3.465 4.961 3.465 4.961 0V29.015c0-1.982 3.455-1.982 3.455 0\"/>",
                "width": 48,
                "height": 48,
                "isSvgEditable": false,
                "isIconNameEditable": false
              }
            },
            {
              "id": 26,
              "title": "2. Sophisticated Botnets",
              "subtitle": "Modern malicious bots don't just click links and leave; they are programmed to mimic human behavior by scrolling pages, pausing, and executing micro-movements with the mouse. They utilize residential proxies to blend in with genuine home users.",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The Clixerfy Defense",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ": Our Behavioral Biometrics Engine detects the mathematical perfection of automated interactions. Even if a bot tricks standard security scripts by routing through a local residential IP, its synthetic behavior instantly gives it away."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "bgimage": null,
              "icon": {
                "iconName": "emojione-monotone:spider-web",
                "iconData": "<path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M62 31.082h-5.261c-6.813-4.749-11.146-12.705-11.618-21.336l2.63-4.825L46.247 4l-2.629 4.829a24.63 24.63 0 0 1-23.238-.002L17.751 4l-1.504.921l2.63 4.827c-.473 8.631-4.805 16.585-11.62 21.334H2v1.839h5.259c6.815 4.746 11.147 12.702 11.618 21.333l-2.63 4.828l1.504.918l2.631-4.829a24.64 24.64 0 0 1 23.234 0L46.247 60l1.504-.918l-2.63-4.826c.473-8.633 4.805-16.589 11.618-21.335H62zm-8.203 0h-5.158c-4.447-3.089-7.272-8.271-7.569-13.896l2.58-4.737c1.032 7.333 4.672 14.021 10.147 18.633M32 30.161l-2.149-3.945a9.4 9.4 0 0 0 2.114.252c.734 0 1.469-.093 2.19-.267zm3.651-3.026a10.6 10.6 0 0 0 2.164 3.947h-4.313zm-5.154 3.947h-4.298a10.65 10.65 0 0 0 2.141-3.961zm0 1.839l-2.148 3.943a10.7 10.7 0 0 0-2.164-3.943zm1.503.918l2.147 3.947a9.3 9.3 0 0 0-4.305.013zm1.502-.918h4.297a10.65 10.65 0 0 0-2.141 3.96zm6.959-1.839c-2.001-1.45-3.288-3.789-3.504-6.348l2.677-4.913c.78 4.373 2.951 8.354 6.132 11.261zm-4.982-7.31a7.71 7.71 0 0 1-6.936.043l-2.677-4.914A17.6 17.6 0 0 0 32 20.012c2.074 0 4.149-.376 6.132-1.111zm-8.461.92c-.185 2.564-1.452 4.913-3.435 6.39h-5.351c3.181-2.905 5.351-6.888 6.132-11.259zm-3.479 8.229c2.001 1.447 3.288 3.786 3.502 6.344l-2.677 4.914c-.781-4.371-2.949-8.354-6.13-11.258zm4.981 7.307a7.72 7.72 0 0 1 6.936-.043l2.676 4.912a17.6 17.6 0 0 0-12.263.003zm8.462-.918c.183-2.562 1.448-4.913 3.432-6.389h5.352c-3.181 2.904-5.352 6.887-6.132 11.26zM32 13.582a26.2 26.2 0 0 0 10.146-2.054l-2.579 4.738a16 16 0 0 1-15.136 0l-2.58-4.738A26.3 26.3 0 0 0 32 13.582m-11.651-1.131l2.58 4.736c-.298 5.625-3.122 10.811-7.567 13.895h-5.16c5.474-4.612 9.116-11.298 10.147-18.631m-10.146 20.47h5.158c4.445 3.086 7.27 8.271 7.567 13.894l-2.58 4.737c-1.03-7.334-4.67-14.022-10.145-18.631m11.648 19.551l2.582-4.738a16.01 16.01 0 0 1 15.134 0l2.579 4.738a26.23 26.23 0 0 0-20.295 0m21.798-.92l-2.58-4.737c.298-5.623 3.122-10.809 7.567-13.894h5.16c-5.474 4.609-9.116 11.297-10.147 18.631\"/>",
                "width": 64,
                "height": 64,
                "isSvgEditable": false,
                "isIconNameEditable": false
              }
            },
            {
              "id": 27,
              "title": "3. Global Click Farms",
              "subtitle": "Click farms employ low-wage workers to manually search for your keywords and interact with your paid ad placements. Because these are real humans sitting at real devices, traditional anti-bot software fails to flag them.",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The Clixerfy Defense",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ": Clixerfy monitors deep Device Fingerprints. If our network flags multiple supposedly unique users sharing identical hardware signatures, or originating from a known click-farm data center range, the entire sector is cleanly neutralized."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "bgimage": null,
              "icon": {
