                "isIconNameEditable": false
              }
            },
            {
              "id": 28,
              "title": "4. Malicious Scrapers & Spiders",
              "subtitle": "Competitors and scrapers use automated programs to crawl your landing pages via paid search or display ads to steal your pricing models, catalog information, and ad copies.",
              "body": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "The Clixerfy Defense",
                      "bold": true
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ": We intelligently separate \"Good Bots\" (like Google’s indexer) from malicious scrapers. The platform allows authorized search spiders to crawl seamlessly while instantly zapping harmful data harvesters."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
